cli.name: component
cli.description: The Component namespace provides commands to retrieve authentication information of a component element

cli.name: list
cli.description: Returns the identifiers for the component elements that have authentication information

cli.name: get
cli.description: Retrieves authentication information about the component element corresponding to component-id

cli.name: fingerprint
cli.description: Retrieves the fingerprint computed from the authentication metadata of the component element corresponding to component-id

cli.name: package
cli.description: The Package namespace provides commands to retrieve authentication information of a package element

cli.name: list
cli.description: Returns the identifiers for the package elements that have authentication information

cli.name: get
cli.description: Retrieves authentication information about the package element corresponding to package-id

cli.name: service
cli.description: The Service namespace provides commands to retrieve authentication information of a service element

cli.name: list
cli.description: Returns the identifiers for the service elements that have authentication information

cli.name: get
cli.description: Retrieves authentication information about the service element corresponding to service-id

cli.name: source
cli.description: The Source namespace provides commands to manage the sources of authentication metadata information

cli.name: create
cli.description: Creates a new metadata source

options.description: English language human readable description of the source
Absolute file path of the metamodel metadata file that has the metamodel information about one component element
Connection information of the remote server

cli.name: delete
cli.description: Deletes an existing authentication metadata source from the infrastructure

cli.name: get
cli.description: Retrieves information about the metadata source corresponding to source-id

cli.name: list
cli.description: Returns the identifiers of the metadata sources currently registered with the infrastructure

cli.name: reload
cli.description: Reloads the authentication metadata from all the metadata sources or of a particular metadata source if source-id is specified

cli.name: fingerprint
cli.description: Returns the aggregate fingerprint of metadata from all the metadata sources or from a particular metadata source if source-id is specified

cli.name: operation
cli.description: The Operation namespace provides commands to retrieve authentication information of an operation element

cli.name: list
cli.description: Returns the identifiers for the operation elements contained in the service element corresponding to service-id that have authentication information

cli.name: get
cli.description: Retrieves the authentication information about an operation element corresponding to operation-id contained in the service element corresponding to service-id

cli.name: command
cli.description: The Command namespace provides commands to get information about command line interface (CLI) commands

cli.name: list
cli.description: Returns the identifiers of all commands, or commands in a specific namespace

options.description: The dot-separated path of the namespace for which command identifiers should be returned

cli.name: get
cli.description: Retrieves information about a command including information about how to execute that command

options.description: The dot-separated path of the namespace containing the command in the CLI command tree

cli.name: fingerprint
cli.description: Returns the aggregate fingerprint of all the command metadata from all the metadata sources

cli.name: namespace
cli.description: The Namespace namespace provides commands to get information about command line interface (CLI) namespaces

cli.name: list
cli.description: Returns the identifiers of all namespaces registered with the infrastructure

cli.name: get
cli.description: Retreives information about a namespace including information about children of that namespace

options.description: The dot-separated path of the namespace containing the namespace in the CLI node tree
The name displayed to the user for this namespace

cli.name: fingerprint
cli.description: Returns the aggregate fingerprint of all the namespace metadata from all the metadata sources
